The US is the mother of wisdom retries:
It is as ridiculous as the schoolgirl snaživostí Barack Obama, the president with a reputation as the smartest, repeated in Afghanistan's ruling the strategy of his predecessor, whom he regarded as the stupidest.
When finally vypotil his eagerly awaited Afghan doctrine, it turned out that it copied over kopírák of Bush's Iraq scenario three years ago.
Not only in the text itself uses the word several times turnover as in Iraq, "but did not hesitate even to use the name of Bush's declaration in January 2007 as the name of their own declaration:" The new way forward ".
Three years ago, at the same time, he criticized Bush's idea to send a fresh military reinforcements to Iraq beset by civil war as "irresponsible and in the aftermath of catastrophic decision".
The subsequent months have shown , however , that the Bush strategy based on a recommendation from the field commanders , was the only possible and , so much so that today in the intelligence on Iraq at all .
Bush's reputation improvement, but objectively left his successor a much passed the default position than it was to be expected.
In Afghanistan he hopes Barack Obama in that the miracle repeats.
The increase military contingent asked him again a field commanders, in particular the supreme commander of the Afghan operation, General Stanley McCristal, which even despite subordinačním harshly criticized the practice hesitant shooter in the White House.
He asked 40 thousand men in order to break the situation for the better.
The president hesitated for three months, but nothing better accrue, so at least fool the general 10 thousand soldiers.
From Europe could squeeze out the promise of further 5 thousands, although he was initially charged with at least 10.
Most problematic for the whole Obama's strategy seems to be his intention to begin withdrawals of troops from Afghanistan as fast as 18 months and terminate the process within three years. Obama's whole doctrine raises more questions than provide answers.
Many doubt that the increase in half-baked fruit gives the same procedure as in Iraq.
Despite the internecine wars of recent years is the Iraqi society relatively well organized, its leaders honor the agreement.
The Afghan situation is characterized by the opposite sign - the one shall not count and no agreements have not been honored.
Wrong, under these conditions, prepare the Afghan security forces used day to change the master in as far as it suits them.
Political institutions, even if they are formally based, will remain just potěmkinovou village, which will continue to could spread patriarchal tribal relations.
Balancing the interests of various ethnic groups is extremely difficult due to clutter ratios, which further complicate the Pakistani and Iranian influences.
Neither the establishment of "akceschopného state", which is a minimalist goal of the entire operation, it doesn't look like all too real.
Obama's strategy at the time horizon .
For the past eight years, the situation in Afghanistan deteriorated only, and is now on the verge of explosion.
Believe in that sending soldiers into a war in order to 'return home early' cause there made a miracle, can only truly romantic soul, the fact untouched.
From a political point of view is to set a date for withdrawal of troops by nezodpovědností, since the Taliban, it will be seen as an implicit admission of defeat.
The last NATO summit showed that the willingness of Europeans to participate in combat operations in Afghanistan is nearing minus.
European politicians can not and do not want to explain to voters how the security of Germany or Italy is linked to the war in the foothills of the Hindu Kush.
Another factor capable of radically to intervene in the situation is developments around Iran.
If the situation continues to deteriorate and intensified sanctions on the Iranians does not produce arises from the United States přetěžká question is, will not try to solve the problem of the use of military force.
To reply to it, it will be in a time when under Obama's America to the vítěznému withdrawal from Afghanistan.
Any such solution, however, will mean a dramatic turn in the Afghan situation.
The only politics for Barack Obama is that the remaining presidential election three years away, so there's still plenty of time to come up with another strategy, if this proves to be a total flop in.
