We can ’ t resign on our production schedule, it is vital, therefore, was designed to be voluntary overtime on Saturday, 19 December, with the result that would have made two shifts, said Vaněk.
The server Sedmička.cz wrote that company employees who work Saturday shift, offered a bonus of CZK 400.
That will get people back to work Saturday, 28 November.
The company is under Vaňka decided to change the way motivating employees for the proposed overtime.
Either you leave to pay extra for overtime or compensatory time off may choose 28th December, and thus about the day to extend the Christmas holidays, said Vanek.
In addition, all the staff Saturday shift will get paid for the fare and lunch.
Whereas the overtime was a point from the point of view of comments and complaints , and employees of protesters , last week halted production , so the management yesterday afternoon decided with immediate effect , the abolition of all the overtime for the month of December , he said .
Staff car companies were last week forced to virtually every day after an eight-hour shift work in a two-hour overtime.
After the signing of the agreement, the union stávkovou emergency appeal
