Managerial revolution or the end of the economic intelligence?
If nothing changes in the management of large French companies, our fight for the development of economic intelligence was unnecessary.
For more than ten years, recalls the behavior management of large company employees access to business-to-consumer marketing before the revolution: the point is to co-identify themselves with the "values" identified from the mountain, as it once was when it was necessary to impose on the consumer products which have emerged heads of the ideas factory technicians.
The fact that the customer has become a hub of entrepreneurial companies, compared the marketing strategy of conquest of the market in the right direction — even if the authoritarian tendencies of the force products different from consumer preferences are regularly.
Passive approach employees can lead to death demoralizaci.
Firms suicides at France Telecom, PSA and Renault are only visible parts of much rozšířenějšího general phenomenon, which will fall mostly managerial cadres.
The demobilisation adversely affects the development of all mental functions of the company, including research and development, and, more importantly, the economic intelligence.
And, indeed, E "requires from all interested parties (...) active approach and the ability to predict a" and requires from the staff of the commitments that are inconsistent with the revenue authoritarian management.
Therefore, we call on the managerial revolution, which should aim to include workers at the center of the interest of the company as a client.
The relative usefulness of internal surveys.
Internal polls - as the questionnaire submitted by employees of the company Orange - will contribute to the revolution in management practices?
Unfortunately I'm afraid not.
Mainly because I convinced myself that in the face of new situation, the structure of the various turning back primarily to the ... you always did!
Furthermore, because the authoritarianism, as one of the pathology of power, shall be increased proportionately with the gravity of their own failures.
And finally, because most of the management of workers has simplified view of human behavior.
Because they are graduates for engineers have mechanical interpretation of psychology.
For reasons of convenience take old behavioristickou theory currently again highlighted "neurovědami" from the US and widely operated without too much knowledge of the scientific institutes and other media.
In fact, it is possible to move the "levers" (sic) the involvement of managers, showed a recent survey agency Ipsos Figaro.fr the site, which only strengthens the management personnel in the position of a mechanical procedure, unsuitable for today's world.
To identify and measure the factors mobilization.
On the contrary, the managerial revolution is necessary for the proper functioning of the modern business, provides for the adoption of definitive vision of human behavior.
Lies in the integration of the basic insight of all projects and practice management: For the employee of the firm commitments will be possible only if they will seem like a simple means to achieve their dreams and ambitions and projects.
Currently, this concept, the motivation of employees engaged in the study only motivation functional analysis.
These studies have shown that evaluates their businesses on the basis of pre-determined doxy, which will allow them through the image, which the company says, assess what offers them to achieve their goals in life.
Thanks to identify and measure of these factors can mobilize managers to monitor, forecast and pre-empted in its "social performance" and list its management of human resources "on the right path".
This creates a breeding ground for the development of a sound and effective economic intelligence.
