Michelin and Fesvial together for the use of helm
Tire manufacturer Michelin, in cooperation with the Spanish Foundation for Traffic Safety (Fesvial) launched a campaign to promote the use of helm, especially for younger motorists, today both of these bodies informed.
The purpose of this initiative is to highlight the importance of the use of helmets , as it is the only means by which we can avoid the head injuries or even deaths in the event of an accident while riding a motorcycle .
The company Michelin indicates that this campaign is part of their obligations regarding the transport safety, which means more than design and manufacture a safer products ", and confirmed that it is trying to fulfil this purpose and otherwise, i.e., in the form of a briefing and information campaigns.
This new campaign to promote the use of helmets when riding a motorcycle, under the slogan 'To be or not to be' is the first phase, in which more than 500 motorcycles will be deployed fixed boards to get to the attention of the general public.
And at the end of the company Michelin has warned that transport safety "is a long-standing problem" of this company, which is the manufacturer of tyres for dvoukolá vehicles and the main aim of which is the continuous improvement of product safety.
The sales of light commercial vehicles
After nearly two years, the market is starting to light commercial vehicles.
All 9.425 vehicles registered in November in Spain meant an increase of 12.6% compared to 2008, and what's more, it was the first increase after 22 months of decline, according to figures patronátní Anfac Ganvam organization of producers and sellers.
The positive figure is better to put in quarantine since November 2008 is very bad period for comparison and marked 60% reduction compared with the previous year.
The consequence is that despite the rise in the last month, the total number of registered vehicles in the last 11 months are 40% less than in the previous financial year.
Since January was prodáno95.853 vehicles, which includes all possible vehicles falling into the category of light commercial vehicles: Derivatives of passenger cars, pick pneuservis less freight cars and light trucks / chassis.
And not even the gloom which harm the demand, even if it is bought by private individuals, most of the purchases were made smaller and medium-sized businesses, and almost 100% of the cases, it is the financing through third parties.
