Thank you
After days of wine and roses since last spring, when inflation assets amounted to the prevailing mood in the markets was once again showed the uncertainty in the markets, which should not be surprising, because it is no longer the natural state in an environment where managers receive a decision on the future, which itself is uncertain.
The drug used by central banks to stabilize the market, it was the liquidation of debt through direct purchases of assets and an indirect free up liquidity at a rate of close to zero, so that financial institutions can buy assets to the deduction.
The central bank has already confirmed that direct purchases of assets has virtually ended, and without being questioned its disparate policy of liquidity, start throwing a bit of sand in the wheels as the Spanish Central Bank, with its auctions in the past year.
Investors, therefore challenge the ability of the world economy to keep the economic recovery without the heterodox measures, and participate in the return of risk reduction benefits.
The volatility in stock markets and the differences dluhopisůspolečností re-gain points, although they are still very remote abnormal levels, which have reached at the beginning of the year.
States were forced to socialize private risk, which again affected the public debt.
Again, the pressure and the quality of the US, Japan and Germany have become a haven for the selected investors, thereby expanding differentiation of euro-zone countries against Germany.
Spain this instability almost was not affected, but at that time came, Standard &amp; Poor's and threatened to new revisions to the reduction in capacity of the Kingdom of Spain.
