Distribution
This apparent paradox is explained by the complex procedure on the distribution of money, which is used by UEFA.
For this financial year authority, chaired by Michel Platini, intends vydělat1.090 million for the Champions League.
Of the money devoted UEFA 413.1 million in fixed payments: each of the 20 clubs that participated in the preliminary round of the classification (including Atletico Madrid) got 2.1 million.
In addition, those who have reached participation, received only $3.8 million for his presence, in addition to other 550.000 euros for every game they are involved in.
