New tools for valuing cars
In these days of storms and accidents earn not only cars.
Every day thousands of cars , which have suffered an event occurring in the service , where expert must estimate the damage and the cost of the repair .
None of the insured event is not the same and the calculation of the cost of the parts and the workforce can be a long and difficult labor.
Manually calculate the cost of the correction from 20,000 to 30,000 euros, including parts and labor, it may take two or three hours.
However, with the support of the new computer tools, it would be a matter of minutes.
Therefore, almost 100% of experts used this type of system.
Suppliers of services and solutions for the estimation of maintenance claims and dedicated to the collection of information by the producers to then draw up and offer its customers a useful tool.
In Spain Audatex, from american group Solera is Head of the company; 80% of the evaluation shall be carried out with its products.
Other companies that compete in the field of valuation and the development of information on the sector, and GtMotive Eurotax.
Working with the data provided by manufacturers, is not simple.
According to Edward Velazquez, commercial director of Audatex, work in Spain, with 63 manufacturers and importers, and every one of them gives them the information in a different format.
In addition, the amount of data for processing is still growing, as in the past five years mentioned multiple versions, variants and motor solution than in the past 15 years.
As soon as the new vehicle will enter the market, these enterprises are to work.
It is a very feverish work, because it is necessary to catalogue every one of the thousands of parts of the vehicle and to determine its value.
In addition, in the case of each model is carried out by an "intelligent" graphic processing ", where it is possible to" put out their "individual parts of tourist cars.
As regards the model with a massive sales, the work can be done in a week, while the process is very fast.
As regards the minority automotive, it may take three or four months. Currently, Audatex is available to complete information about 99.2% of the cars sold in Spain.
Among the most exclusive models, which have information include Porsche, but not as Ferrari or Lamborghini.
Regarding mobile park in circulation exceeds 99%.
To perform the work of the document and the development of the database has Audatex eight houses grouped around the world (Spain, France, Germany, the US, Brazil, Mexico, China, and Japan), and each of them specializes in particular brands.
National headquarters is in Alcobendas (Madrid).
There is more than one hundred technicians (normally experts on drive) has been working at the same time, with three computer screens.
Audatex invests 90 million euros a year to develop these databases.
Each month, sets of data and 2.5 million customers receive updates every two days.
Processing of this great stream of information allows firms to different uses, and the provision of various products.
The most common use focus on repair and maintenance, but also by individual countries, there are tools for the management of spare parts, or for the calculation of the sales or the residual value of the car.
The firm, which is available in the guide, which shall inform the value of used vehicles in Spain, is Eurotax.
Audatex is in our country offers, but in the United States, yes.
With regard to the products, which offers Audatex, it is easy to get the support that can be used by professionals in the sector.
The firm offers ten různýchnástrojů, while the product is the star AudaPlus, standard solutions to the valuation of claims for an expert.
Includes cars, motorcycles and light and heavy industrial vehicles.
In addition to the cost of parts also includes time to correct the estimated by the manufacturer or lakovnou.
This instrument shall be paid according to use for each evaluation.
The highest price is 5.75 euros for customers who use little more than ten times a month.
Then every insurance undertaking which carries out the thousands of estimates, negotiate their price with the Audatex.
Other products such as AudaVIN allow full identification of vehicles and equipment, with whom he worked on the assembly line, but only on the basis of the chassis.
AudaGlass focus on glass vehicles and AudaSubastas service is open to the professional sector on the Internet, which allows you to disable a vehicle with an insurance event.
The statistical service is very useful for identifying the trend to perform geodemografických analyses or deviations by makes and models.
For example, it is possible to study how much modelůurčité brands has undergone service because of the accident, or how many suffered serious claims for a certain period of time.
GT Motive is the only Spanish firm, which is dedicated to the development of this type of instruments.
Among other things, sells Gt Estimate, who is also specified for experts and so provides digital images, access to parts or prices and the official time of the manufacturer.
GT is a company group based in 1971 as a supplier of services and solutions to assess the damage , accidents or maintenance of cars
GT GUÍA valuation is its historical reference product on the market.
They work with 24,000 users in garages 3.100 experts and 53 insurance companies.
The volume of sales rose by 20% a year for the last three years and in 2008 were charged by 10.8 million.
At the beginning of last year, began the process of internationalisation installing an office in Paris.
Audatex originated in Germany in 1966 and in 1979 became established in Spain.
According to sources of 62% of its bratu arises in Europe and 38% in North and South America. Working with 900 insurance companies and 33.000 services, of which 3,000 in Spain.
World Billing Group Solera (Audatex, Sidex, Informex ABZ, Hollander and IMS) to reach 557 million U.S. dollars, which is 3.3% more than in 2008.
In our country the company earned 19.1 million euros, which is 7.2% more than last year.
In 2005, the Group 1. Stood on the exchange of 1.000 million, and now has its shares are estimated at a total value of 2.400 million.
Since 2007, listed on the New York Stock Exchange and is included in the reference index, Standard & Poor's.
