Manages about 3,000 daily ads and on the Spanish market has added about 100 new ads every day.
Under Spanish law, a car whose chassis number has been discarded, can't go into operation, but it can be used as a source of spare parts, which were not damaged.
Vehicles with historical value may be allowed to operate, although they were discarded after preliminary proceedings.
The budget of the service in four steps
With the tool Aouda-taller firm Audatex guarantees that the user gets budget of only four steps: Identification of the vehicle, the search for a replacement part, create a budget agenerování budget.
Ease of use is an essential condition for such systems, mainly for the belief in a higher age professionals who, to a greater or lesser extent tend to be reserved for the use of new management techniques.
The database contains 1.034 vehicles, of the tourist 666, 109 field, 137, 78 of supply and 44 of the trucks.
Naturally , it should be for the use of the computer with a connection to the Internet .
After identification of the model, which has been assigned to repair, using the chassis number, the real graphical display model, and then select the needed a spare part.
The user can include variables, such as the price of labor, overtime or discounts, and then print and passed on to the customer.
AudaTaller is a tool for measuring as AudaPlus, but rather a reference catalog.
The main difference between the two systems is that it is oriented on service and does not include an estimate of the labour force.
The cost of the use of this instrument for the workshop are 350 euros per year, which the client may finance.
